        2322,
        1412,
        1264,
        1412
      ],
      "ignore": false,
      "order": "17",
      "anno_id": 1,
      "text": "models operating \"on the edge\" in this resource constrained system. In addition, we develop a client-server application for real-time bug detection, integrating the ML models to provide accessible results to farmers. Lastly, we explore effective postharvesting strategies using SWIR-HSI images to detect insect punctures invisible to the naked eye, thereby enhancing the quality of marketable fruit.",
      "line_with_spans": [
