      "anno_id": 1,
      "text": "To address the challenges posed by BMSB, and in particular those related to computer vision, HALY.ID proposes to leverage machine learning  $(ML)$  technologies [4] in the following research activities.",
      "line_with_spans": [
        {
          "category_type": "text_span",
